title: ChatGPT's Performance Is Slipping, New Study Says
description: UC Berkeley researchers found that ChatGPT has not improved over time, and in fact, may have gotten worse.

title: Tesla reports no change to $184M Bitcoin holdings amidst record $25B revenue
description:
Tesla reported no change to its digital asset holdings during its Q2 2023 investor report, as seen in its shareholder deck on July 19.
